&lt;p&gt;In this role, you will assist with managing and coordinating activities of a service team to ensure that all upkeep, inventory and repair of grounds and buildings of the property are completed in an efficient manner, as well as working as part of the team to complete all maintenance duties.&lt;/p&gt;
