&lt;p&gt;Do you have strong plumbing, electrical and HVAC trade skills? Do you like interacting with people and being in a customer service role? If you have demonstrated leadership skills, top notch technical skills and a commitment to quality service for your residents, &lt;strong&gt;Weinstein Properties&lt;/strong&gt; is the place for you! &lt;em&gt;Apartment Maintenance Supervisor experience required.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
