&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Schedule:&lt;/strong&gt; Working hours are 8 AM to 5 PM Monday - Friday. This position requires participating in an emergency on-call rotation with your teammates, bonus paid when on call.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Requirements:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
